# Volatile runtime state: per-session JSON, locks, telemetry, and the
# legacy pre-Option-B task work dir. Tracked work products live under
# .claude-hooks/work/ and .claude-hooks/archive/ (NOT inside state/) so
# they survive in source control as evidence trails. Do NOT add work/
# or archive/ to this list.
.claude-hooks/state/
*.bak.*
